OL,3,CAid worker from Jersey receives
OL,4,Cpersonal letter from The King
OL,6,FAn aid worker from Jersey has received
OL,7,Fa handwritten letter from His Majesty
OL,8,Fthe King honouring his courage.
OL,10,FSimon Boas, who is the Executive
OL,11,FDirector of the charity Jersey
OL,12,FOverseas Aid, received the note on
OL,13,FThursday 11th July.
OL,15,FIt was hand-delivered on behalf of
OL,16,FKing Charles III by His Excellency,
OL,17,FThe Lieutenant Governor, Vice Admiral
OL,18,FJerry Kyd CBE.
