OL,3,CAid worker from Jersey receives
OL,4,Cpersonal letter from The King
OL,6,FThe letter expressed how moved His
OL,7,FMajesty had been after hearing of
OL,8,FSimon's "courageous approach" to his
OL,9,Fcancer diagnosis and his services to
OL,10,Fcharities.
OL,12,FSimon was diagnosed with cancer in
OL,13,FSeptember 2023 and has written letters
OL,14,Fto a local newspaper detailing his
OL,15,Ftreatment, which have received
OL,16,Fhundreds of thousands of views online.
