OL,3,CAid worker from Jersey receives
OL,4,Cpersonal letter from The King
OL,6,FDue to his openness about disease,
OL,7,Fhe's received a number of award
OL,8,Fincluding: the Bailiffs Silver Seal
OL,9,Fand the Certificate of Achievement
OL,10,Ffrom the World Jersey Cattle Bureau.
OL,12,FSimon has also written a book
OL,13,Faddressing the topic of cancer and
OL,14,Fdeath titled; 'A Beginner's Guide to
OL,15,FDying' which will be published in
OL,16,FSeptember.
OL,18,FThe letter was received ahead of The
OL,19,FKing and Queen arriving in Jersey on
OL,20,FMonday 15 July before heading off to
OL,21,FGuernsey the day after.
